<div class='documentTop'><div>
  
  
    <h1>Starting a company/entrepreneurship</h1>
  
  </div></div>
  

  <div class="documentBody" id="Tekstinnhold">   
  <div>
    <p><strong>Entrepreneurship is paramount for the exploitation of resources among local populations, to help create attractive jobs close to local communities and to increase added value.</strong></p>
<p>The Ministry of Local Government and Regional Development plans to pave the way for entrepreneurs to realise their goals and set up new companies. This is of particular importance in areas with low diversity of commerce in order to ensure a more varied labour market and to develop good, dynamic commercial environments.</p>
<p><strong>The Ministry has four central target areas related to entrepreneurship:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Promoting a culture of entrepreneurship</li>
<li>Guidance and increasing competencies</li>
<li>Funding schemes for companies in the early stages</li>
<li>Infrastructure, preparation and networking.</li></ul>
<p><strong>Young</strong> <strong>people and women</strong><br />The government attaches particular importance to providing young people and women with the opportunity to create their own place of work. It is the government’s objective to promote genuine opportunities for motivated young people to work and live outside of densely populated and large urban areas. Women and young people represent an essential resource, with the potential to contribute towards added value and the development of attractive local communities. In 2008, the government launched its Plan of Action for increased entrepreneurship among women, comprising a number of specific measures to reinforce entrepreneurship among women. This will be followed in 2009 by a plan of action for entrepreneurship within education.</p>
<p><strong>Implementation</strong><br />The specific measures are primaily implemented by local, regional and national bodies. A large share of the work involved is financed by funds channelled via the county authorities.<br /></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.innovasjonnorge.no/Om-oss/Innovation-Norway/How-to-start-and-run-an-enterprise-in-Norway/" target="_blank">How to start and run and entreprise in Norway</a> (Innovation Norway)</li></ul>
  </div>
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
